title: About Me
text:
My name is Mandeep and I’m currently pursuing a Masters in Data Science and Computational Linguistics at UBC. I’m passionate about AI and its potential to transform the world.



Masters in Data Science and Computational Linguistics, UBC (2023 - present)
Bachelor of Science in Computer Science, Thapar University (2019 - 2023)





Programming languages: Python, C++
Machine learning frameworks: TensorFlow, PyTorch, Scikit-learn
Natural language processing tools: NLTK, spaCy, Gensim
